{"tid":1500282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對抗狗鐵！！！全民跳閘！！！","createTime":"2019-08-24T03:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T05:24:56.000Z","uid":10457,"like":139,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"4c0b154a05503ba360d4f5394b52ccc68fd82a57","tid":1500282,"uid":10457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:43:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190824&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59968179\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190824%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59968179&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLsTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=9f243de6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190824%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59968179&h=f9234abe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190824&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59968179</a> <br />\n【逆權運動】為防示威衝擊 港鐵正午起彩虹至調景嶺站停駛 九龍灣至藍田封站<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家一齊攬撚炒！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">全民跳閘</span></span><br />\n<br />\n政府同狗鐵有意串通！元朗太古葵青 大家有目共睹<br />\n<br />\n我地就連狗鐵都反埋<br />\n<br />\n有手足或者市民唔夠膽跳<br />\n<br />\n就約埋一班一齊跳<br />\n<br />\n再唔係就一齊守閘比人直行直過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先開錯台 依家開返個新"},{"pid":"54cc5e350a793f249ecf47c027bb3beaba599416","tid":1500282,"uid":10457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:44:42.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"748ac496c7a1ad096263769badd77d32efaf4d5b","tid":1500282,"uid":164239,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:44:59.000Z","msg":"幫推， 歡迎copy and paste<br />\n<br />\n觀塘要人！！！各區去觀塘巴士：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屯門南 259D<br />\n屯門北 258D<br />\n天水圍 269C<br />\n元朗 268C<br />\n東涌 E22<br />\n大埔 74X<br />\n上水 277E<br />\n粉嶺 277X<br />\n沙田市中心 88X/89<br />\n第一城 89X<br />\n沙田圍 89B/80X<br />\n大圍 80/89B<br />\n馬鞍山 89D<br />\n大水坑/石門 89C<br />\n九龍塘 E22<br />\n旺角 1A/13D/16/296C<br />\n佐敦 1A/14/W2<br />\n尖沙咀 1A/215X/219X<br />\n紅磡 11X/15<br />\n土瓜灣 11X/14/15<br />\n將軍澳 296A/296C(尚德)/98A(坑口寶琳)<br />\n深水埗/長沙灣 296C<br />\n中西區 101<br />\n灣仔 101/601/619<br />\n銅鑼灣 601/619<br />\n北角 601/619/小輪<br />\n東區 606/小輪(西灣河)<br />\n南區 671<br />\n黃大仙 (求其一架新界嚟嘅)<br />\n九龍灣 (行啦屌你)"},{"pid":"b06c1c4471bdfefa224e378fb4ac4e5d1e37be6b","tid":1500282,"uid":123870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:45:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38e64c75c4ae245b8946d7f716b59af22d4133f6","tid":1500282,"uid":10457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:45:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">全民跳閘</span></span>"},{"pid":"8c4cf615f5249f9061a4ed777dab3ae644e4f5ca","tid":1500282,"uid":10457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:45:20.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"6aae5b76326dd5a01840a6acfb9d9c166cad264e","tid":1500282,"uid":10457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:45:32.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"3aa73415f5ef13a70d02d64fcdb506b56932ab27","tid":1500282,"uid":225977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:45:42.000Z","msg":"彩虹跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad7122fc69ba750d9545e8bab9d21d6d5d0bd8a","tid":1500282,"uid":279145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:45:42.000Z","msg":"完完全全唔買任可，港鐵係業主的店的東西！"},{"pid":"84cc9350527a04560749125297276ba3a04932ea","tid":1500282,"uid":10457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:45:43.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"62372165fe00cc0b5fa4d1ca4820e5c2697985b7","tid":1500282,"uid":266683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim